description.content:
Hello,

Are you tired of using different CMS for website development that has thousands of plugins, subscriptions, and limitations?


And now you are looking for something special that has no limitations so that you can build any features and build your dream business website or web application, using custom code.


*charges are Flexible* - It's important to note that my charges are flexible, depending on the task's complexity or the number of pages required


My skills: 


Reactjs

Hooks

Reactstrap

Redux

HTML

CSS

Javascript

Bootstrap

Sass/Scss

Redux toolkit

Ant design (antd)

Socket io

Typescript

Tailwind

Nextjs


If you order this gig:


you'll receive 100% quality work that aligns with your requirements.

you can rest assured that your project will be delivered within your budget.

I write clean and readable code that is easy to modify in the future if needed.

Please don't hesitate to contact me before placing an order to discuss your project's specifics.
